- incluir plan do terraform com os serviços: RDS, memcache e redis
- provisionamento do serviço (no kubernetes) na hora da criação do app/pod

- Recriar cluster de prd
```
export KUBE_AWS_ZONE=sa-east-1a
export AWS_S3_REGION=sa-east-1
export NUM_NODES=2
export MASTER_SIZE=m3.medium
export NODE_SIZE=m3.large
export KUBE_ENABLE_NODE_PUBLIC_IP=true
export KUBE_ENABLE_CLUSTER_REGISTRY=true
export KUBERNETES_PROVIDER=aws
export KUBERNETES_SKIP_DOWNLOAD=true
export KUBE_ENABLE_NODE_AUTOSCALER=true 
export KUBE_ENABLE_DAEMONSET=true #Adicionado para funcionamento do WeaveScope Probe
export NON_MASQUERADE_CIDR="172.16.0.0/14" #Alterado devido overlap da subnet 10.0.0.0/8 com VPCs existentes.
export SERVICE_CLUSTER_IP_RANGE="172.16.0.0/16"  #Alterado devido overlap da subnet 10.0.0.0/8 com VPCs existentes.
export DNS_SERVER_IP="172.16.0.10" #Alterado devido overlap da subnet 10.0.0.0/8 com VPCs existentes.
export MASTER_IP_RANGE="172.17.0.0/24" #Alterado devido overlap da subnet 10.0.0.0/8 com VPCs existentes.
export CLUSTER_IP_RANGE="172.18.0.0/16" #Alterado devido overlap da subnet 10.0.0.0/8 com VPCs existentes.
```
- Criar/Usar chaves do user Kubernetes
- Alterar scripts nodes
  - Instalar Sysdig
  - Criar kube-registry-proxy
  - Instalar WeaveScope
  - Criar script bootstrap no s3 --> Caso precisarmos adicionar algo no bootstrap do nodes, precisaremos somente alterar o script do S3.
  
  
